name: A.L.I.C.E.
description:
The A.I. named A.L.I.C.E. wants to create a new safe world for human beings but an error thwarts her plans.

Try to die as long as possible while the time countdown gets faster by each death through the rooms.

The A.I. A.L.I.C.E. stays positve and claims that a end of a test is a new test and restarts over and over.
